Teltoli

(OOC: Nearly no one replied to my posts.. so I'm gonna change them..)

Teltoli flies in beast mode over the forest, knowing it was now officially R&R time. She looks down as she flies over a lake near the Ark, with a beautiful waterfall and trees around it. 

It had pure clear water.. just right for having a splash around in! She dives down and into the water, landing with a splash. With a loud yell of happiness, she flops onto her back and uses her wings to keep her afloat on the surface. 

This was the life! The battle had been one big tension ride for her.. she needed relaxation!
